Warriors of the French Foreign Legion

War Documentary hosted by Will Lyman, published by Discovery Channel in 2002 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/0/0d/Warriors-of-the-French-Foreign-Legion-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

The Legion is an army surrounded by romance, myth and intrigue. Its history spans more than a hundred and fifty years. The Legion is world renowned for its bravery. The legions motto is simple: Legio Patria Nester - The Legion Is Our Country. The Legion never leave their weapons behind, and never fail to take an objective. Death comes first.
